'People forget, for those of us who weren't selected this summer to play in Brazil, it's not only difficult for us, it's difficult for our families,' he said. 

'In many instances, our families had this amazing vacation trip of a lifetime planned, and that was taken from them.'

'Although I didn't agree with the decision and I still know I should have been there, it was also good for me to say, you know what, it's not always going to go your way.

